Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmng...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahí...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,¡Alto!
